Class ProjectModelToDatabaseListener

ProjectModelResolutionListener
public class ProjectModelToDatabaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements ProjectModelResolutionListener

Just in Time save of project models to the database, implemented as a listener on ProjectModelResolver objects that implement FilesystemBasedResolver.
